			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">When using this data set for Life Cycle Assessment, ensure that the system boundaries include the mechanical compression and dewatering of sludge as well as the drying and incineration phases. Modeling the transport and handling within the plant is also essential. The functional unit should be consistently applied as 1 ton of wet sludge post-mechanical compression. Users should give special consideration to the emissions produced during the incineration phase and contemplate potential energy recovery aspects, which could influence the overall environmental impact assessment.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">在使用此数据集进行生命周期评估时，请确保系统边界包括污泥的机械压缩脱水以及干化和焚烧阶段。模拟工厂内的运输和处理也是必须的。功能单元应以机械压缩后的1吨湿污泥为准一致应用。用户应特别考虑焚烧阶段产生的排放，并考虑潜在的能源回收方面，这可能会影响整体环境影响评估。</useAdviceForDataSet>
